{
  "stem": "9728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As many as they could-- as they could put it in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no room to stand, not only to sit down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, let me just point out before this, coming back to Rumkowski.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rumkowski was the elder-- the chief honcho in the-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they deported, they liquidated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't know even that he is going to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When he was deported, he had such a pull that they said either he, through his pull, or they told him that he is going to be the chief in that new camp, that he did not go in our cattle wagon, but they attached a special railroad car.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the whole clique, he and his chiefs from [INAUDIBLE], went in that railroad car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he came to Auschwitz-- as a matter of fact, let me point it out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Birkenau is a camp two miles away from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Auschwitz was the camp where they gassed and killed the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They gassed them and they burned them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They cremated them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, Birkenau was a camp that supplied the people to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If Auschwitz could not kill-- gas and kill so many.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we were-- and Birkenau was the transitional camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we came to Birk-- when Rumkowski came to Birkenau, he got up, he got the same treatment as anybody else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when we came into Birkenau our first order was take your clothing off, put your baggage away-- we never saw it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Take your everything off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In the nude.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Men and women, everyone in the nude.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 19 September 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was so-so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not cold, not warm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just mild.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
